OL,5,G1900 FIFA WC2026: Switzerland v Canada
OL,6,     FSwitzerland v Canada (Kick-off
OL,7,     F8.00pm). Mark Pougatch presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of both teams' concluding
OL,9,     FGroup B match, held at BC Place
OL,10,     FVancouver in Canada. The only
OL,11,     Fprevious meeting between these
OL,12,     Fnations was a friendly match in
OL,13,     F2002 that took place on Swiss
OL,14,     Fsoil, and saw the Canadians claim
OL,15,     Fa 3-1 victory. This time around,
OL,16,     Fboth teams look all but certain to
OL,17,     Fadvance to the last 32 after each
OL,18,     Ftaking four points from their
OL,19,     Fmatches against Bosnia and
OL,20,     FHerzegovina and Qatar, with the
OL,21,     Fco-hosts just needing a draw to
OL,22,     Fguarantee top spot due to their
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
