OL,7,G2320 The Assembly
OL,8,     FDavid Tennant takes part in the
OL,9,     Finnovative interview show in which
OL,10,     Fhe is questioned by an audience of
OL,11,     Finquisitive individuals who are
OL,12,     Fautistic, neurodivergent and/or
OL,13,     Flearning disabled. Does he believe
OL,14,     Fin God? How did it feel to lose
OL,15,     Fhis parents? Does he know how to
OL,16,     Fvogue? From his skincare regime to
OL,17,     Fhis cancelled friend, no subject
OL,18,     Fis out of bounds
