OL,5,G2345 The Assembly
OL,6,     FSinger Jade Thirlwall faces the
OL,7,     Fgrilling of a lifetime from an
OL,8,     Faudience of autistic and
OL,9,     Flearning-disabled interviewers.
OL,10,     FDoes she regret selling her soul?
OL,11,     FWere the pyramids created by
OL,12,     Faliens? Does she get trapped wind?
OL,13,     FNo question or line of enquiry is
OL,14,     Foff the table. Expect revelation,
OL,15,     Fchaos and a lot of laughs
