OL,5,G0300 British Touring Car Championship
OL,6,G     Highlights
OL,7,     FNicki Shields presents action from
OL,8,     Fthe 10th, 11th and 12th races of
OL,9,     Fthe campaign, which came from
OL,10,     FOulton Park. Championship leader
OL,11,     FAsh Sutton came into the race
OL,12,     Fweekend with a dominant 50-point
OL,13,     Flead over rival Tom Ingram,
OL,14,     Ffollowing his win and second-place
OL,15,     Ffinish at Snetterton. With
OL,16,     Fcommentary by David Addison and
OL,17,     FTim Harvey
